<!-- ============================================================
     ADD CARD  |  Owner: Ryan (Student B - Adding Information)

     Posts to: POST /add-card
     Form tag MUST have enctype="multipart/form-data" or the image
     never arrives and req.file is undefined with no error.

     FIELDS (name= must match exactly):
       card_name        text      required
       genre_id         DROPDOWN  required  <- from genres table
       category         free text required  e.g. Pokemon, NBA
       condition_id     DROPDOWN  required  <- from conditions table,
                                  ORDER BY condition_rank
       rarity           free text optional  e.g. Holo Rare, Rookie
       purchase_price   number    required  step="0.01" min="0"
       estimated_value  number    required  step="0.01" min="0"
       quantity         number    required  min="1", default 1
       remarks          textarea  optional
       image            file      optional

     NOT on the form:
       user_id     comes from req.session.user.user_id -- never a
                   hidden field, that could be edited in DevTools
       date_added  the database fills it (DEFAULT curdate())
       card_id     AUTO_INCREMENT

     Only TWO dropdowns: genre_id and condition_id. Both must be read
     from the database, not hardcoded -- the spec gives no marks for
     hardcoded content, and they must reflect what the admin curates.
     ============================================================ -->


